---
// src/components/StoryCooking.astro
---
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-appleGray-50 dark:bg-appleGray-950 border-t border-appleGray-200 dark:border-appleGray-800">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-16">
    <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
      <span class="text-indigo-500 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Chapter 04</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">My Cooking Skills</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-appleGray-600 dark:text-appleGray-400 leading-relaxed font-light">
        I find magic in the kitchen. Experimenting with fresh ingredients, perfecting old family recipes, and presenting dishes beautifully is one of my favorite escapes. It's an art form you can taste.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 w-full grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
      <div class="space-y-4 lg:space-y-6">
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547592180-85f173990554?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cooking Prep" class="zoomable w-full h-56 sm:h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow" />
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1482049016688-2d3e1b311543?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Pasta Dish" class="zoomable w-full h-40 sm:h-48 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow" />
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 lg:space-y-6 mt-8 lg:mt-12">
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490818387583-1b5f2b011197?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Healthy Bowl" class="zoomable w-full h-40 sm:h-48 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow" />
         <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466637574441-749b8f19452f?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cooking action" class="zoomable w-full h-56 sm:h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl cursor-zoom-in shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
